Reminder

  - Install X11: pacman -S xorg-xinit xorg-server xorg-server-utils
  - Install display driver: pacman -S xf86-video-fbdev xf86-video-mesa
  - Install Desktop & Login Manager
  - Set in xorg.conf keyboard es
  - In /boot/config.txt
    ·  Change overscan
    ·  hdmi_drive=x
       - Where 'x' corresponds to:
         0 for Auto
         1 for Analog out
         3 for HDMI

